QuestData.Title: Dimensius the All-Devouring
QuestData.Description: Your brave actions have forced Ameer to react! He has deployed Captain Saeed and the Avengers!$B$BNow all that is left to do is destroy Dimensius.$B$BWhen you are ready, I will call for Saeed. If he is not currently fighting another battle, he will be awaiting orders from you - directly east of here.$B$BLet him know when you are ready to fight and he will put his troops in motion!$B$BI wish you luck, fleshling! We have hunted Dimensius for a thousand years!
QuestData.LogDescription: Professor Dabiri at the Protectorate Watch Post in Netherstorm wants you to speak with Captain Saeed and then follow his army to Manaforge Ultris and kill Dimensius the All-Devouring!
QuestData.RewardText: For a thousand years, all we have known is conflict. We have defended our people from the attacks of both void creature and ethereal alike.$B$BNow, one of our most hated enemies lies dead - finally.$B$BI give you the thanks of a hundred million ethereals, fleshling.
